            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Plugin registry/search is not in scope. But a builtin, minimal \"plugin manager\" based on https://github.com/savq/paq-nvim is in scope. Current status/plan is here:\r\n\r\n- https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/24221#issuecomment-1616009906\r\n- https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/20893#issuecomment-1297870788\r\n\r\nThese use-cases are in scope:\r\n\r\n- Reduce the steps needed to install plugins (or other plugin managers) from a URL.\r\n- Establish a provider-like interface for \"plugin install\" task.\r\n\r\nNothing else is in scope, please don't leave comments on those issues, they'll be deleted.",
